rComments: Lectures are boring, but he explains concepts pretty well if you can stay awake. Tests are usually very short and easy, but small mistakes can hurt you big time. Uses weird-ass conventions that no other professors use. About 5 hours of homework a week.
Lots of Fun, espically if you enjoy 5 hour homework assignments and one question tests.
Boring as hell lecturing.  Tests problems are too complicated for the time allowed.
Explains things very well in lecture.  Beard is always neatly trimmed.
